  "description": "A vibrant ruby-throated hummingbird perches on a thin, dark brown branch against a clear, bright blue sky. The hummingbird's throat is a striking iridescent ruby red, contrasting with its emerald green back and dark wings. The bird is in profile, looking slightly upward. A small, partially visible green leaf is present in the upper right corner. The branch extends diagonally from the lower left to the upper right, appearing somewhat delicate.",
